  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Embark on an epic journey with <strong>Nyran Survivors</strong>, an action-packed roguelite where you'll confront endless hordes of foes and take on formidable bosses. Unleash powerful skills, evolve your character and master ancient spells. Earn spoils from each battle to unlock new classes, upgrade your abilities, and forge a path to become the ultimate Mediator.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/77a7b326ff7649fa9220d3c53d874467.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/77a7b326ff7649fa9220d3c53d874467.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/77a7b326ff7649fa9220d3c53d874467.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose your path from an array of distinct classes, each offering unparalleled abilities. Play up to <strong>11</strong> classes with more on the horizon over <strong>2</strong> game modes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/a4db8bc63e24f78dc3b1a8cef8fbb690.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/a4db8bc63e24f78dc3b1a8cef8fbb690.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/a4db8bc63e24f78dc3b1a8cef8fbb690.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Over <strong>80 items</strong> for you to equip with more along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skills</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/60a41fb217c21d48f1eeb20cf695bb1f.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/60a41fb217c21d48f1eeb20cf695bb1f.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/60a41fb217c21d48f1eeb20cf695bb1f.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nyran Survivors has over <strong>100 unique spells and abilities</strong> for you to collect and master with more to come!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss Fights</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/ed388ec692329d2f0d258032eb52c3a8.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/ed388ec692329d2f0d258032eb52c3a8.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/ed388ec692329d2f0d258032eb52c3a8.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>6 unique bosses</strong> per map for you to defeat for a total of <strong>30 bosses</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/c5d446fe2d2aa716fb4c21b9e6742f5b.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/c5d446fe2d2aa716fb4c21b9e6742f5b.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/c5d446fe2d2aa716fb4c21b9e6742f5b.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade your class through <strong>40 levels</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Passives</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/fc9a9f2bd3919dd59d8f01ee63a45c9b.poster.avif?t=1724984840\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/fc9a9f2bd3919dd59d8f01ee63a45c9b.webm?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540810/extras/fc9a9f2bd3919dd59d8f01ee63a45c9b.mp4?t=1724984840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Select from a variety of <strong>12</strong> distinct passives to enhance your abilities throughout the battle, with the option to have 3 active simultaneously.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboards</h2>Can you secure the top spot and become a true legend? Let your name shine on the global stage of Nyran Survivors! The game lists the top 100 players' rating per map.<br><br><i>* uses a logged in Discord account</i>",
